Conclusion

A decentralized lending protocol is built on a few core ideas:

Liquidity pools

Algorithmic interest rates

Over-collateralized borrowing

Automated liquidation

These mechanisms allow the system to operate without centralized intermediaries.

Understanding these fundamentals is essential for building or auditing DeFi lending systems.

